To create a smoother/solver,

1. instantiate the common class solver

   solver = new MLI_Solver_Construct( solver_id );
  
   where solver_id is one of :

      MLI_SOLVER_JACOBI_ID    : 301
      MLI_SOLVER_GS_ID        : 302
      MLI_SOLVER_SGS_ID       : 303
      MLI_SOLVER_PARASAILS_ID : 304
      MLI_SOLVER_SCHWARZ_ID   : 305
      MLI_SOLVER_MLS_ID       : 306
      MLI_SOLVER_SUPERLU_ID   : 307

2. call setParams to set specific parameters

   solver->setParams( param_string, argc, argv );

3. call setup

   solver->setup();

4. call solve

   solver->solve(MLI_Vector *, MLI_Vector *);

